## SplitsContract.distribute() method

Distribute Funds

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
distribute(): TransactionResultPromise;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

TransactionResultPromise

## Remarks

Distribute funds held by the contract in the native currency to all recipients.

## Example


```javascript
await contract.distribute();
```
